  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Anyway-- I didn't learn them all, but I learned a little bit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so my father, in, in Vilna, was still living away from us, living undercover.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because he was afraid that he would be caught and that two and two would be added and who he really was-- a prominent anti-communist-- would be discovered.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But lo and behold, a few months after we've applied, there was our name, granting us permission to leave.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we hurriedly made the preparations, bought the tickets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The tickets would require that we go to Moscow, because in Moscow we could catch the trans-Siberian train that would take us to Vladivostok, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on the border of the Japanese ocean and there-- from there be transported by boat to Japan.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So that began in December of 1940.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was an overnight trip to Moscow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only we left, because we had the visa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were, of course, permanent citizens of, of Vilna, without any intention of leaving.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, to leave where you live, you had to have a desperate motivation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No one knew what was in store for those who didn't leave.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No one could imagine the atrocities that were forthcoming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No one could imagine the horror of the war that was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was much more likely that you could survive better staying in, in your house in, in, in the surroundings you knew best with the language and people that could protect you better than to go off into the unknown, where no one was certain of a destiny at all if you could survive the travels and the dangers of travel during a time of war.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So those that were running were really a small percentage of the population.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
